- Use secure payment gateways and ensure PCI compliance.
- Implement webhooks for real-time payment status updates.
- Validate payment data on the server-side to prevent tampering.
- Provide clear user feedback during the payment process to enhance user experience.
- Log payment transactions for auditing and troubleshooting purposes.